<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361442" n="1"/>
<opener> <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> et <abbr>Sapientiss.</abbr> Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs> </opener>
    <p><lb/>Priusquam responsum<del> a Te</del> accipiam ad <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517054805501">literas</rs> quas ad Te dedi hebdomada
                              <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terita, te rogare audeo Vir Amiciss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi> ut cogites etiam de <choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>is qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perlegi in 
                              <lb/><rs key="biblio_E7R5XBJH" type="biblio"><abbr>Theatr.</abbr> <abbr>Anat.</abbr></rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104347945" type="person"><abbr>Joh.</abbr> <abbr>Jac.</abbr> Mangeti</rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que huc traduco. Si enim aliquos detegas errores
                              <lb/>magis magisque compescam <add>in mea <rs type="biblio">opella</rs></add> arrogantiam <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-116372354" type="person">Astruc</rs> <add>Galli</add> qui (referente <rs key="pers_DE-588-104347945" type="person">Mangeto</rs>)
                              <lb/>in sua <rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio"><abbr>Dissertat.</abbr> de Motu Musculorum</rs> non uti debebat adeo honorific<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>
                              <lb/><subst><del>loquitur</del><add>locutus fuit</add></subst> de <abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cellentiss.</abbr> Patruo tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanne</rs>, a quo tamen si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habet bona
                              <lb/>imo melior<subst><del>e</del><add>a</add></subst> exscripsit. Prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> igitur <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-116372354" type="person">Astruc</rs> <subst><del>ponit demonstrare conatur</del><add>supponit verum</add></subst>
<lb/>sequens lemma.</p>
<p><lb/><cit type="long"><quote>Cavitatem quamcunque <formula>BED</formula> liquido plenam, <figure facs="../images/figures/1361442_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-102552517"><figDesc>Schematische Darstellung eines Gefässes mit schmaler Öffnung.</figDesc><note type="editorial">Es handelt sich um eine Nachzeichnung der Figur 5, Tab. 1 in <rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio">Astruc 1710</rs>.</note></figure>
<lb/>et in quam per canaliculum <formula>ABCD</formula> novum
                              <lb/>influat liquidum, pressionem in quibuslibet punctis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem experiri, sin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gulasque ejusdem partes, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> canalis <formula>ABCD</formula> amplitudini pares sint, vi tota
                              <lb/>et energi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> liquidi per hunc canalem influentis extrorsum propelli.<del> No</del>
<lb/>Notior (inquit <rs key="pers_DE-588-116372354" type="person">Astruc</rs>) et vulgatior est ea propositio quam ut in illa probanda
                              <lb/>frustra tempus teramus.</quote><bibl><rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio">Astruc 1710</rs>, pp. 93-94.</bibl></cit></p>
<p><lb/>Mihi autem non adeo vera videtur h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c propositio. Quum enim pressiones
                              <lb/>et gravitationes liquorum in qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque plana horizontalia propor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionales sint altitudinibus liquor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> super his planis; falsum videtur,
                              <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales<del> pression</del> impressiones fieri in singulas cavitatis <formula>BED</formula> partes <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                              <lb/><del>liquido </del>novo liquido influente per canaliculum <formula>ABCD</formula>. Nam etiamsi vi
                              <lb/>liquidi de novo influentis pressio et gravitatio in cavitatis <formula>BED</formula>
<lb/>singulas partes esset eadem, diversa tamen esse debet vi diversarum
                              <lb/>altitudinum liquoris quo cavitas ipsa <formula>BED</formula> plena supponitur antequam
                              <lb/>novum influat liquidum per canaliculum <formula>ABCD</formula>.</p>
<p><lb/>Probare contendens latera vesicular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> muscularium in circulum ab influen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>te Sanguine inflari, hanc dat demonstrationem. <cit type="long"><quote>Sit Curva <formula>CBD</formula>, cuius
                              <lb/>singula puncta a potentiis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualibus <figure facs="../images/figures/1361442_02.png" hand="pers_DE-588-102552517"><figDesc/><note type="editorial">Es handelt sich um eine Nachzeichnung der Figur 8, Tab. 2 in <rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio">Astruc 1710</rs>.</note></figure>
<lb/><formula>AB</formula>, <formula>LK</formula>, <formula>HG</formula> <abbr>etc.</abbr> perpendiculariter
                              <lb/>premantur. Evidens est, centrum
                              <lb/>gravitatis <choice><orig><g ref="#omn">õ</g></orig><reg>omn</reg></choice>ium harum potentiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>,
                              <lb/>quibus tota Curva premitur esse in linea <formula>AB</formula>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in punctum Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>medium <formula>B</formula> perpendiculariter agit.
                              <pb facs="1361443" n="2"/>
<lb/>Sed ex his qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in re simili de Chordarum in Parabolam, Hyperbolam et Ellipsim
    <lb/>incurvatione demonstravit <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-123249201" type="person">Pardies</rs> in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_SEJZTZGQ">Statica</rs> <abbr>n.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> 70 debet eadem linea, quam
                              <lb/>commune gravitatis centrum potentiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> omni<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> hinc inde agenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> dirigitur,
                              <lb/>transire per concurs<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>E</formula> tangenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> punctis <formula>C</formula>, <formula>D</formula> curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ducuntur. Linea ergo
                              <lb/><formula>AB</formula>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mediam Curvam <formula>CD</formula> perpendiculariter secat, per tangenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> quoque con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cursum<del> <formula>E</formula></del> <formula>E</formula> perductur. Pari prorsus modo centr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> gravitatis potentiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>partem Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BD</formula> premunt in linea <formula>HG</formula> erit, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> puncto intermedio <formula>G</formula> insistit,
                              <lb/>eaque linea per concurs<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>F</formula> tangenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>BF</formula>, <formula>DF</formula> a curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> extremitatibus <formula>B</formula>, <formula>D</formula>
<lb/>ductar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> transibit. Similiter centr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> gravitatis potentiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>partes <formula>BG</formula>, <formula>GD</formula> gravitant in lineis intermediis et perpendicularibus <formula>LK</formula>, <formula>ON</formula>
<lb/>futurum est, line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tangentes ab extremis Curvarum <formula>BG</formula>,<del> <formula>GID</formula></del> <formula>GD</formula><del> punctis</del>
<lb/>partibus ductas in communi concursu intersecabunt, atque sic de c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teris
                              <lb/>minoribus Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> portionibus. Ver<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Geometris evidens est circular<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>solam esse, in qua recta a tangenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> concursu ducta, curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> partem tan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gentibus intercept<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> perpendiculariter semper bisecet.</quote><bibl><rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio">Astruc 1710</rs>, pp. 102-104.</bibl></cit> Ergo <abbr>etc.</abbr></p>
<p><lb/>Subdit postea <rs key="pers_DE-588-116372354" type="person">Astruc</rs>. <cit type="long"><quote>Proposit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> lemma jampridem demonstravit
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobus Bernoulli</rs>in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8PKSE46C">Regulis quas ad determinand<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> veli curvaturam</rs>
<lb/>edidit in Actis Lipsiensibus <date when="1692-05"><abbr>an.</abbr> 1692 Mense Maio</date>. Demonstravit quoque
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Joannes Bernoulli</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobi</rs> Frater in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_JAFFCHKU"><abbr>Dissert.</abbr> de Motu Musculorum</rs>, sed uterque
                              <lb/>abstrusiore et operosiore methodo, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> differentialem et integralem cal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>culum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>supponat, unde lector<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> labori atque studio parcere et planio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem facilioremque demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> proponere visum est.</quote><bibl><rs key="biblio_7GZ89GM9" type="biblio">Astruc 1710</rs>, pp. 105.</bibl></cit></p> <closer><salute>Vale
    <lb/>mihique impera.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1718-06-08"><abbr>a. d.</abbr> 8 Junii 1718</date></dateline>.</closer>
<lb/><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1718-06-09">9<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date>.</foreign></note>
<postscript><p>
<lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr>
<lb/>Te rogo ut<del> hanc</del> ejusmodi demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <add>attent<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></add> perpendas mihique tuum
                              <lb/>de illa judici<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> communices necessaria figura apposit<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>.</p></postscript>
